k placed beside the bowl" class="wp-image-88790" srcset="https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-1.jpg 1200w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-1-500x500.jpg 500w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-1-860x860.jpg 860w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-1-400x400.jpg 400w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-1-96x96.jpg 96w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-1-378x378.jpg 378w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-1-276x276.jpg 276w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-1-600x600.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1200" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%201200%201200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="whisk resting inside a metal bowl with blended dry ingredients" class="wp-image-88791" data-lazy-srcset="https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2.jpg 1200w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2-500x500.jpg 500w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2-860x860.jpg 860w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2-150x150.jpg 150w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2-400x400.jpg 400w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2-300x300.jpg 300w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2-96x96.jpg 96w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2-378x378.jpg 378w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2-276x276.jpg 276w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2-600x600.jpg 600w" data-lazy-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-lazy-src="https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2.jpg" /><noscript><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1200" src="https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2.jpg" alt="whisk resting inside a metal bowl with blended dry ingredients" class="wp-image-88791" srcset="https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2.jpg 1200w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2-500x500.jpg 500w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2-860x860.jpg 860w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2-150x150.jpg 150w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2-400x400.jpg 400w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2-300x300.jpg 300w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2-96x96.jpg 96w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2-378x378.jpg 378w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2-276x276.jpg 276w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-2-600x600.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>
</div>
</div>



<p><strong>Combine the blackberries and dry mixture</strong><br>To the large bowl with most of the dry topping ingredients, add the blackberries and toss them to coat well. Toss carefully so you don't break them.</p>



<p><strong>Transfer to the baking dish<br></strong>Transfer the coated blackberries to a prepared 9-inch square stoneware baking dish and spread into an even layer.</p>



<p><strong>Repeat with the raspberries</strong><br>Toss the raspberries with the reserved dry ingredients in the small bowl, and place them evenly on top of the blackberries already in the baking dish. Scatter any remaining dry ingredients from either mixing bowl evenly on top of the berries to absorb liquid as it's released in the oven.</p>



