eside the bowl" class="wp-image-88795" srcset="https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-7.jpg 1200w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-7-500x500.jpg 500w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-7-860x860.jpg 860w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-7-150x150.jpg 150w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-7-400x400.jpg 400w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-7-300x300.jpg 300w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-7-96x96.jpg 96w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-7-378x378.jpg 378w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-7-276x276.jpg 276w, https://glutenfreeonashoestring.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Gluten-free-blackberry-cobbler-step-7-600x600.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></noscript></figure>
