	<div class="wprm-recipe-summary wprm-block-text-normal"><span style="display: block;">This gluten free blackberry cobbler has a jammy, sweet-tart filling and a soft biscuit topping that bakes up golden and tender. This reliable recipe works even when your berries aren’t perfect.</span></div>
